{"type":null,"faqId":33404,"title":"通话过程中不能锁屏且没有锁屏音","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.38402778in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>通话过程中，能否锁屏要依据手机当前设置的解锁样式来确定。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>当解锁样式是“华为解锁”和“无密码”时，通话过程按电源键，仅熄灭/点亮屏幕，不锁屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>当解锁样式是“图案解锁”、“数字密码”、“指纹解锁”等密码锁时，通话过程按电源键，会锁屏且熄灭/点亮屏幕，但无锁屏音。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8106","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748601000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"通话,锁屏","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}